  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0ddc \u0db6\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d91\u0db4\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Half of the whites are tired of Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Tourism Development Authority Chairperson Mrs Dhammika Wijesinghe told Lankadeepa that about 45 percent of the hotel reservations made by foreign tourists before coming to Sri Lanka have been suddenly canceled due to the struggles.",
        "It had a very negative impact on the tourism industry and lack of fuel, gas and electricity cuts were another major reason for the decrease in tourist arrivals.",
        "Mrs. Wijesinghe said that the arrival of tourists has increased by ten percent so far this month, forty two thousand nine hundred and twenty five tourists have arrived so far.",
        "Generally, these days, the number of tourists who come on a weekday (average value) is 1533. Mrs. Dhammika Wijesinghe said that it was 1900 on a weekend day.",
        "The Director General said that August is usually the time when more tourists come to Sri Lanka, so a special program was started to attract more tourists to the country during that time.",
        "Mrs. Wijesinghe said that a tourism promotion program has been started targeting the Kandy Perahara to attract tourists and mentioned that they are also working to provide various other facilities including providing fuel for the transportation of tourists.",
        "The largest number of tourists this month came from England. That number is 8304.",
        "After that, the largest group of tourists came from India and the number is 5416.",
        "In addition to this, the Director General further mentioned that more tourists have come to this country from countries like Germany, France and Canada."
      ],
